---
title: Italian Beef Meatballs & Chickpeas with Cherry Tomatoes and Arugula
description: This hearty and refreshing salad may be low on carbs, but it's packed with flavour! Meatballs and tomatoes bring the cozy-factor to this soon- to-be weeknight favorite.

